downloadDescription: This zipped folder contains several presentations to provide an overview of Azure Dev-test offerngs for CSP partners.
detailsSection:
This zipped folder contains several presentations to provide an overview of Azure Dev-test offerngs for CSP partners. This includes
1. Why Azure for dev-test - which gives an overview of Azure's dev-test capabilities for customers and partners
2. How can partners make money doing dev-test on Azure - This presentation provides a deep dive on Azure's capabilities for application development and testing, and how partners can make money by launching Dev-test as a service
3. Sharepoint dev-test on Azure -- This presentation provides an overview of Azure's capabilities for application development and testing, with deep dive into Sharepoint dev and test
